3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
4. the dancer is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |
| Hobby      | reading    | woodworking      |
| Food          | asparagus | pomegranate |
| Job           | nurse     | dancer      |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | disco       |
